result.content:
salam :)
nomre hatun ziad bad nis vali asanam khub nis.
sa'y konin azmune ba'di ye nomreye motma'en begirin o tori nabashe ke kolli az un chizi ke fekr mikardin kamtar shin akhare azmun
unaii ham ke bug ziad mizanan ru badihi zadan bishtar kaar konan.

natayej: http://pastebin.ubuntu.com/9271613/

judge va codatun: http://bayanbox.ir/info/3917253589738581003/judge

g++ judge.cpp -O2 -ojudge
./judge <inp
